Add your steps (pseudo-code) for the dice game here.

Display greetings
Display the rules of the game
Ask the player whether he/she wants to start the game
Take input from the player
IF the player wants to start the game
     Set playing to true
     Starts the game
     WHILE playing is true
         Rolls the dice
         Display the results of the rolled dice
         Display what the results means (win,lose or establishes a point)
         IF the player wins (sum of the rolled dice is 7 or 11)
             Display congratulations
             Ask the player if he/she wants to play again
             IF yes
                 continues the loop
             IF no
                 breaks the loop
                 display thanks message
         IF the player loses (sumod the rolled dice is 2 or 3 or 12)
             Display Sorry You Lost
             Ask the player whether to continue with the game
             IF yes
                 continues the loop
             IF no
                 breaks the loop
                 displays thanks message
         IF the player neither win or lose
             Establishes a point
             Display the point to the player
             Player needs get the same sum in the next roll to win
             Ask the player to continue
             IF yes
                 continues the loop
             IF no
                 breaks the loop
                 displays thanks message
            

IF the player does not want to start the game
    Display see you later message


